This is a game of 100 to 1, also known as Family Feud
The goal is to answer a given question in a way that aligns with the way most of the 100 randomly asked people answered it.
____
To run this game you need Python 3+ installed along with Flask, Flask-WTF, Flask-SQLAlchemy and Flask-Migrate.
After cloning the repository run (in shell from the game's root directory)
- set FLASK_APP=game.py (for Windows. For Linux use 'export' instead of 'set')
- flask db init
- flask db migrate
- flask db upgrade
- python db_setup.py
- flask run